Description: Create a directory, populate it with data, build models,
    forecast rodent populations, and visualize the results. The user can
    spin up a local lightweight sandbox or full scale production environment
    from the same code underlying the continuously deployed Portal Predictions
    Project continuous integration system
    <https://github.com/weecology/portal-forecasts> and website
    <https://portal.naturecast.org>.
URL: https://weecology.github.io/portalcasting/,
    https://github.com/weecology/portalcasting
